Global Electric Power Trowel Machine Market Insights
Electric Power Trowel Machine Market size was valued at USD 0.85 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Electric Power Trowel Machine Market Overview
The electric power trowel machine market has experienced significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for efficient and high-performance construction equipment. The global market is valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5%. This growth is largely attributed to the rising construction industry, the demand for faster and smoother concrete finishing, and the push towards automation in construction processes. The Asia-Pacific region is expected to lead the market due to large-scale infrastructure developments, followed by North America and Europe.

